{"tid":2213068,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"龐氏騙局 越滾越大爆煲","createTime":"2020-09-22T09:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T11:09:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1a49e777d98815010d58aab15a7c8a31adba8b6e","tid":2213068,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:19:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200922/3WXL4HTQCRBYDD3TQ6DYSYUZOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200922%2F3WXL4HTQCRBYDD3TQ6DYSYUZOY%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I20xj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=963fdc59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200922%2F3WXL4HTQCRBYDD3TQ6DYSYUZOY%2F&h=8bf934b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200922/3WXL4HTQCRBYDD3TQ6DYSYUZOY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n龐氏騙局 越滾越大爆煲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Oa850vWXlWHygXAOMca_4xk5Cj0=/1878x2449/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/M7GRI5QTWJDDPDDNGZ4OHMNNCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOa850vWXlWHygXAOMca_4xk5Cj0%3D%2F1878x2449%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FM7GRI5QTWJDDPDDNGZ4OHMNNCA.jpg&h=83e1e400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬多夫<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美斥縱容金融犯罪 中擬列不可靠清單  腹背受敵 滙控穿$30<br />\n<br />\n「龐氏騙局」是一種金融欺詐手法，主要以一些虛假甚至不存在的獲利機會吸引群眾投資，其方法是不斷找來投資者注資，並以這些資金當作利潤及回報支付給早期投資者。然而當尾隨加入的投資者越來越少，騙局便會因資金入不敷支而爆破。<br />\n<br />\n龐氏騙局是由一位叫龐氏（Ponzi）的意大利人發揚光大。。。。。。。。。。。。龐氏過了一年奢華日子後遭報紙揭發，根本沒在相關公司投下任何資金，結果被判詐騙罪入獄。<br />\n<br />\n近年較著名的龐氏騙局為馬多夫騙案，2008年金融海嘯前後被揭發，涉及金額達500億元，不少富豪亦被騙，次年馬多夫被判刑150年，滙控亦因而捲入訴訟，至今仍在處理中。"},{"pid":"c2784ad28e0d4a575ec011f8456df10656b91b56","tid":2213068,"uid":279606,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:25:42.000Z","msg":"龐氏騙局 不如叫層壓式騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\npreserve埋實際意思添"},{"pid":"cb65f860317fc813fdc2da7cb15e0e9c1c3bf3e7","tid":2213068,"uid":237425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c2784ad28e0d4a575ec011f8456df10656b91b56","tid":2213068,"uid":279606,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:25:42.000Z","msg":"龐氏騙局 不如叫層壓式騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\npreserve埋實際意思添"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:27:19.000Z","msg":"響香港一講層壓式就知係咩<br />\n十個有八個人都應該遇過"},{"pid":"d82a65fe331fddc87cacb7601a6b94b2c71f6a87","tid":2213068,"uid":78336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c2784ad28e0d4a575ec011f8456df10656b91b56","tid":2213068,"uid":279606,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:25:42.000Z","msg":"龐氏騙局 不如叫層壓式騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\npreserve埋實際意思添"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T10:15:18.000Z","msg":"畢氏定理不如叫直角三角形兩短邊與長邊關係定理，preserve埋意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n海底奇兵不如叫海底都是魚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da851295928b817138b043c5a2f995517405929","tid":2213068,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d82a65fe331fddc87cacb7601a6b94b2c71f6a87","tid":2213068,"uid":78336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c2784ad28e0d4a575ec011f8456df10656b91b56","tid":2213068,"uid":279606,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:25:42.000Z","msg":"龐氏騙局 不如叫層壓式騙局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\npreserve埋實際意思添"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T10:15:18.000Z","msg":"畢氏定理不如叫直角三角形兩短邊與長邊關係定理，preserve埋意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n海底奇兵不如叫海底都是魚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T10:17:25.000Z","msg":